<p>Simply in <strong>JavaScript</strong>, you can redirect to a specific page by using the following:</p>

<pre><code>window.location.replace("http://www.test.com");
</code></pre>

<p>Or</p>

<pre><code>location.replace("http://www.test.com");
</code></pre>

<p>Or</p>

<pre><code>window.location.href = "http://www.test.com";
</code></pre>

<p><strong>Using jQuery:</strong></p>

<pre><code>$(window).attr("location","http://www.test.com");
</code></pre>
